      <description>About me Hello! I am a master student in Microelectronic Engineering Department at Huazhong University of Science &amp;amp; Technology(HUST). Currently, I am advised by Dr.Xiaowei Xu and I am doing research in CPSIL lab led by Professor Yu Hu. My research focus is on time series data miming and embedded computing. We hope to design new optimized and energy-efficiency embedded architecture to accelerate distance function in data miming and apply deep learning algorithms to solve real world problems.</description>
